overview: The user initiated a request for a complete aesthetic overhaul of
  their sleep questionnaire application, noting its current "okay" but
  uninspired appearance. The agent began with a thorough review of the app's
  existing visual elements, identifying areas such as the generic color palette,
  plain backgrounds, dense form sections, and lack of visual personality as key
  improvement opportunities. The approach involved a systematic update, starting
  with a new sleep-themed color palette featuring deep indigo/purple tones and
  soft teal accents. This was followed by significant refinements to the main
  questionnaire form, including a more engaging progress bar and enhanced card
  styling with subtle background patterns. The introduction section was
  transformed into a welcoming hero experience with feature cards, and
  individual form components like checkboxes, radio groups, and sliders received
  a polished, modern look. Finally, the report section was updated with
  consistent themed styling, resulting in a more cohesive, calming, and
  professional user interface tailored for a sleep assessment experience.
